snippet.title: This Keyword in Java - How to use "this"
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast

- This is the "this" keyword in java. It makes it easier to set variables in classes. 

Learn java in just 13 minutes: https://youtu.be/RRubcjpTkks

This in java is simply a keyword you use to set variables in classes.

The "this" java keyword can be tricky at first... But SURELY you'll get it :) If you followed along, congrats! You learned by-doing!

I hope you enjoyed this "this" keyword in java video! I like to have a nice mix of java tutorials and actual projects for you all :)
